author: Deepika Jayaram
title: Jomonte Suviseshangal enters 30 crore club | Malayalam Movie News
text:
Actor Dulquer Salmaan 's film Jomonte Suviseshangal was released after a prolonged wait, just after the strike between producers and theatre owners was called off. And as they say good things come for people who wait, it looks like the saying has come true for the makers of the film.
Jomonte Suviseshangal has recently entered the 30 crore club, as it fetched around 32 crore. Apparently, this will be the fourth film of Dulquer Salmaan to have joined the league. Other films of the actor in the same group are Charlie, Bangalore Days and OK Kanmani.
